  <description>
    <p>Oboete is a straightforward and efficient flashcard application designed to help users
      study and memorize information effectively. Whether you're learning a new language,
      studying for exams, or just trying to remember important facts, Oboete provides an
      intuitive platform for creating, organizing, and reviewing flashcards.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Study flashcards with ease</li>
      <li>Fast and easy to use</li>
      <li>Works out of the box</li>
      <li>Can import flashcards from other sources such as Anki</li>
      <li>Does NOT sync to the cloud</li>
      <li>Image and FSRS support</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This app has been developed with libcosmic for the COSMICâ„¢ desktop, and issues may occur on
      other platforms</p>
  </description>

